On the Using AppLinks to link to other applications page (under Installing JIRA applications - Extending JIRA applications) it says from Administration to go to Add-ons then select Application Links in the left menu. In fact you get to the Application links page From Applications, not Add-ons. Also the page name does not have all initial caps, only the first word.

See https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/AdminJIRAServer070/Using+AppLinks+to+link+to+other+applications

