As noted in JRA-44017, when editing the Description or Comment fields of an issue inline, drag and drop attaches the file to the issue and embeds the image in the text simultaneously. When editing those same fields in a lightbox (e.g. Create or Edit pop-ups), drag and drop attaches the file to the issue and stops there. The attachment must then be manually selected via the WYSIWYG button in order to embed it in a text field.

