I was wondering if it would be feasible to add a step in the upgrade/update process, from say 7.0.x to 7.0.x that you would have a question near the end that says move back the modified files listed that were custom/changed.

Something that allows that flexiblity to be part of the process rather than something manual afterwards. But put that power into the admins hands to say yes or no there.

just something to think about.

