I've been trying to import a project in JIRA from an old instance for a while. The issue has been the speed of my IT dept is slower than your releases. We keep running into a build number mismatch.

JIRA should be able to import projects from the same version number. Differences between builds (especially ONE BUILD) shouldn't make a difference and be prevented.

Having this limitation just makes things extremely difficult.

