We are having major JIRA server migration and planning to use the existing database for new JIRA server. We are planning to get the database backup also. We have few clarifications.

1. If we copy existing JIRA_HOME into new server and configure to existing database, do we need to manually enter the licences ?
2. If we fail the new server in case, we need to restore the old (existing) server, in this case do we need to restore the database from the backup we already got or can we use the existing database?

